rComments: Kind of a jackass but very knowledgeable, articulate, confident (verging on cocky). not very receptive to other point of views, thinks he is always right which doesn't create the greatest atmosphere for discussions. has fed govt and int'l connections.

Don Hubert is GOD. He perhaps could've put more effort into our class, but it's understandable because he was too busy saving the world. He has a lot of experience in the field, which is fascinating to hear about. He brought some great guest speakers as well.
